actionName: Check the functionality of 10F1 MCB in bottom cabinet. Replace it if required.
actionExplanation:
When 10F1 is ON and 10F1:2,4,6 is having 230V AC available, 10F1:1,3,5 should also have 230V AC available. If 230V AC is missing at�10F1:1,3,5 then replace the 10F1.
If 10F1 is keep tripping then disconnect the connections from 10F1:1,3,5 and turn it ON again.�If it trips again then replace the 10F1.
